description:
Service Usage

CDH will send a subset of biometric collection information to ICSE using this service. This information will include a CSP URL link which will enable the ICSE VPO to view all the biometric collection event information for that client, as stored in CDH.

Service Usage

CDH will send a subset of biometric collection information to ICSE using this service. This information will include a CSP URL link which will enable the ICSE VPO to view all the biometric collection event information for that client, as stored in CDH.
